{
  "stem": "5626.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were assigned to a barrack, which was really a barn before the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we lived over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were put together again, a big group from different directions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we had Hitlerjugends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were our guards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were even younger than we are, and they all carried a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Funny, it sounds very funny, but sometimes when we went out to work, these Hitlerjugend asked us if we would carry his machine gun because it's too heavy for him to carry.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was the funny part of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That was the first time in my life where I was restricted to one meal a day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We got the meal at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In the morning when we went out to work, we all got a piece of German Brot, brown bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But they-- that was our meal, our food for the whole day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that night when we came back, we got the usually dinner, a very big soup.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And sometimes we got some potato.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I think once a week, we got meat also.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were working on, on the borderline.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They said that the Russian army is coming, and we have to dig big, big foxholes for them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So when the tanks will come, the tank will fall into these holes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That will stop-- at least, that's what they thought-- that will stop the, the Russian arm, which is coming down from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we worked over there until about a month.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That's when we started a march.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They didn't tell us where are we going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They put the group together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They exchanged the Hitlerjugend for SS soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we started the March.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "First time, first day, second day, third day, it was almost fun, like we went for a, an outing.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
